frac8:val = {2, 3, 5};  // 2 3/5

// Dynamic construction
tbb8:w = 1;
tbb8:n = 1;
tbb8:d = 2;
frac8:dynamic = {w, n, d};  // 1 1/2 (runtime values)
```

