## String Representation

```aria
frac64:gdp = {23000000000000, 5, 10};  // $23 trillion + $0.50
gdp.write_to(stdout);  // Output: "23000000000000 1/2"

frac64:pi = {3, 5419351, 1725033};  // π approximation
pi.write_to(stdout);  // Output: "3 5419351/1725033"

