## Constrained Generic Structs

```aria
// T must implement Display
struct Printable<T> where T: Display {
    value: T
}

impl<T> Printable<T> where T: Display {
    fn print() {
        print(self.value);
        println("\n");
    }
}

// Works - i32 implements Display
